# Copy to /srv/ddns/secrets.env on natto, populate, chmod 0600 (root:root).
# Read by the cloudflare-ddns container via docker-compose's env_file.
#
# DO NOT COMMIT THE POPULATED VERSION (services/ddns/.gitignore excludes it).
#
# Create the token at: Cloudflare dashboard → My Profile → API Tokens →
# Create Token → "Edit zone DNS" template. Scope it as narrowly as possible:
#   Permissions:  Zone → DNS → Edit
#   Zone Resources: Include → Specific zone → nthncrtr.com
# This token can rewrite DNS for the zone, nothing else. It is the only
# automation credential that touches Cloudflare; treat it accordingly.

CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
